===Noun phrase===
'''Big Bang'''
{{wikipedia}}
#The scientific name given to the cosmic event that marks the beginning of Time and the rapid expansion of Space for the visible [[universe]].  The evolution of the universe since that beginning point is described by the Big Bang Theory.

